<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>118</hymn_number>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Aize! ka Khamhtu Bawi thisen, Keimah ca'h a chuak maw? Santlai lo kei
 ruangah hin maw, A lu sung a pek ko?

[V2]
 Keimah nun sualpalh ca ah maw? Vailam thing cung a hram, Khuaruahhar
 zaangfah le velngeih, Dawtnak chim khawh lo cu.

[V3]
 Zeizong vialte Sertu Bawi Khrih, A rak thih lio ah khan, Lei le van
 nih an hramh dih i, Ni zong kha a tlang lo.

[V4]
 Ngaihchiat mitthli cham khawh lomi, Dawtnak lei ka bat cang, Bawipa,
 ka pum pe hmanhning law, Cu nih a rul kho lo.</lyrics>
<title>AIZE! KA KHAMHTU THISEN A CHUAK MAW? CH118</title>
</song>